00052 {
00053     int *pinv ;     /* inverse row perm. for QR, fill red. perm for Chol */

00056     int *cp ;       /* column pointers for Cholesky, row counts for QR */
00057     int *leftmost ; /* leftmost[i] = min(find(A(i,:))), for QR */

00059     double lnz ;    /* # entries in L for LU or Cholesky; in V for QR */
